{"tid":1468971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大家當自己係中國人？","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:13:18.000Z","uid":270525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2f2f113f5dad7425564f14a33986a3662a91fb","tid":1468971,"uid":270525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">只有一件事想講，用字。<br />\n<br />\n停止使用「大陸/內地」，<br />\n用「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅大陸係連接鄰國嘅新界及九龍半島<br />\n<br />\n用「中國」係顯示明確嘅領土觀念<br />\n<br />\n你係香港人，<br />\n香港就係你嘅祖國(Motherland)<br />\n<br />\n唔係「大陸」<br />\n<br />\n你經過邊境，<br />\n係由「中國海關」檢疫，<br />\n唔係「大陸海關」。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩用字遣詞似番個香港人<br />\n<br />\n你唔會「返大陸」嘅，<br />\n你會去「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"601a82256b82e7be1d6c01fd29a957c68aae90c8","tid":1468971,"uid":270525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:42.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"f03cf93869aeb4f57d62ba9b7bcb273cf1017fb3","tid":1468971,"uid":230051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd2f2f113f5dad7425564f14a33986a3662a91fb","tid":1468971,"uid":270525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">只有一件事想講，用字。<br />\n<br />\n停止使用「大陸/內地」，<br />\n用「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅大陸係連接鄰國嘅新界及九龍半島<br />\n<br />\n用「中國」係顯示明確嘅領土觀念<br />\n<br />\n你係香港人，<br />\n香港就係你嘅祖國(Motherland)<br />\n<br />\n唔係「大陸」<br />\n<br />\n你經過邊境，<br />\n係由「中國海關」檢疫，<br />\n唔係「大陸海關」。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩用字遣詞似番個香港人<br />\n<br />\n你唔會「返大陸」嘅，<br />\n你會去「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"Jo mud 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6323ec580714b9a8b9280438a16dacff849fef","tid":1468971,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:51:14.000Z","msg":"用開支那 支國 強國 贏國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f196048634689e0dfb1d2f9c08f81aa